          <tr>
          <td align="left" valign="center">
          <font size="+1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#F52E00>
          <b>Specifications</b>
          </font>
          </td>
          </tr>
          <tr><td colspan=2 height=1><img src=../../../img/blank.gif width=1 height=1></td></tr>
          <tr><td height=4><img src="../../../img/blank.gif" width=1 height=4></td></tr>
        </table>
        <table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=4>
          <tr>
          <td valign="">
          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#555555>
          <ul>
            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Device</div><a href="../index.htm">Operative surveillance camera</a>            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Purpose</div>Covert photography            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Model</div>NAILON, &#1053;&#1040;&#1048;&#1051;&#1054;&#1053;            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Manufacturer</div><span class="short" aria-label="Mechanical Factory of Krasnogorsk (KMZ, Zenit)" data-balloon-pos="up"><a href="../../../manuf/kmz/index.htm" class="short" >KMZ</a></span>            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Year</div>1975            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Country</div><a href="../../../spy/glossary.htm#soviet">Soviet Union (USSR)</a>            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Predecessor</div><a href="../f21">AJAX-12 (F-21)</a>            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Successor</div><a href="../f27">NEOZIT (F-27)</a>            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Shutter</div>Electronically controlled            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Lens</div>Special NL type            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;"><span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Depth Of Field">DOF</span></div>1.3 m - &infin; (see Distance)            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Lens angle</div>56&#176;            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Speed</div>1/15 to 1/250 sec            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Aperture</div>f/2.9, f/5.6, f/16            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Distance</div>4-28m (f/2.9), 2.8m-&infin; (f/5.6), 1.32m-&infin; (f/16)            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Film</div>KN-2, sliced 21 mm            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Frame</div>18 x 24 mm            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Exposures</div>14 (600 mm of film)            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Sensitivity</div><a href="#spec_sens">see below</a>            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Advance</div>0.7 sec (spring motor operated)            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Power</div>2.7V/<span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Direct Current (battery)">DC</span> (2 &#215; 1.35V mercury button cell), or<br /><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;"></div>2.5V/<span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Direct Current (battery)">DC</span> (2 &#215; 1.25V type D-0.02 rechargeable cell)            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Dimensions</div>77 &#215; 57 &#215; 41 mm            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Weight</div>250 g          </ul>
</font></td></tr></table>        <a name=spec_sens></a>
